name: CREATE R Workshop
tagline: Introduction to R for Ecological Data Analysis workshop at the Canadian Rivers Institute of the University of New Brunswick.
body: # README Lindsay Brin Materials for the **Introduction to R for Ecological Data Analysis** workshop at the Canadian Rivers Institute of the University of New Brunswick. "Lessons_Outline" gives an outline of the workshop flow, which includes lessons based on Data Carpentry materials as well as lessons that I developed.
